          "page_number": 2,
          "block_type": "text",
          "block_type_cn": "文本",
          "text_content": "Umen \\(+\\) (Beijing Ruixun Lingtong Technology Co., Ltd.), with the mission of \"data intelligence, drives the growth of business\", is based on outstanding technologies and computing algorithm capabilities, combines with real- time multidomain data resources, provides Internet enterprises with statistical analysis, operation, and technological effective improvement tools, and provides brand owners with online and offline digital intelligent marketing services, to assist the business in continuous growth.",
