          "page_number": 2,
          "block_type": "text",
          "block_type_cn": "文本",
          "text_content": "Up to Jun. 2021, Umen \\(+\\) has provided professional data services over ten years for accumulative 2.3 million mobile applications and 9.5 million websites, covering 191 industry categories and outputting more than 300 analytical indicators for applications or industries. The typical customers are including CCTV, the Client- end of People's Daily, Toutiao, Himalaya, Chang Ba, Quick Hand, Easyhome, Intime Department Store, and so on.",
          "bbox": {
