          "block_type": "text",
          "block_type_cn": "文本",
          "text_content": "In Jul. 2019, the intelligent services of Umen \\(+\\) data were upgraded strategically, and Umen \\(+\\) Cloud - data intelligent cloud services for Internet enterprises, was launched. Through integrating leading cloud technologies and aggregating ecological service resources, it has achieved the cloud services of collection, storage, modeling, data management and data application, and fully supported the seamless integration of business data and behavioral data of Internet enterprises, accelerating the process of enterprise intelligence and driving business growth.",
