      "markdown_text": "=====================\n\nBASE:  torch.Size([1, 256, 1280])\n\nPATCHES:  torch.Size([6, 100, 1280])\n\n=====================\n\nTranslation  \n\nAbout UsUmen \\(+\\) Product Developer Center Community Brand News Compliance Zone Shopping within RMB100  \n\n# Umen \\(+\\) , the Domestic Leading Third-party Intelligent Provider of Multidomain Data  \n\nUmen \\(+\\) (Beijing Ruixun Lingtong Technology Co., Ltd.), with the mission of \"data intelligence, drives the growth of business\", is based on outstanding technologies and computing algorithm capabilities, combines with real- time multidomain data resources, provides Internet enterprises with statistical analysis, operation, and technological effective improvement tools, and provides brand owners with online and offline digital intelligent marketing services, to assist the business in continuous growth.  \n\nUp to Jun. 2021, Umen \\(+\\) has provided professional data services over ten years for accumulative 2.3 million mobile applications and 9.5 million websites, covering 191 industry categories and outputting more than 300 analytical indicators for applications or industries. The typical customers are including CCTV, the Client- end of People's Daily, Toutiao, Himalaya, Chang Ba, Quick Hand, Easyhome, Intime Department Store, and so on.  \n\nIn Jul. 2019, the intelligent services of Umen \\(+\\) data were upgraded strategically, and Umen \\(+\\) Cloud - data intelligent cloud services for Internet enterprises, was launched. Through integrating leading cloud technologies and aggregating ecological service resources, it has achieved the cloud services of collection, storage, modeling, data management and data application, and fully supported the seamless integration of business data and behavioral data of Internet enterprises, accelerating the process of enterprise intelligence and driving business growth.  \n\nIn Sep. 2019, Umen \\(+\\) obtained the ISO/IEC 27001:2013 Information Security https://www.Umen \\(+\\) .com/page/about"
    },
